Italy's wholesale price index rose 0.2 pctmonth-on-month in February 1987 after increasing by 1.1 pct inJanuary, the national statistics institute ISTAT said.    The index, base 1980 equals 100, registered 173.1 inFebruary compared with 172.8 in January.    The February figure represents a decline of 0.2 pctcompared with February 1986 after a year-on-year decline inJanuary 1987 of 1.7 pct.                       Reuter&#3;